Name            : MK MOOSA KASIM
Date            : 29-12-2021
Description     : A02 WAP to generate Fibonacci numbers., Generating a series of fibonacci numbers by adding first two number from the series and generating it as per the user instruction till where. using loops and if-else condiitons.
Input           : Enter a number: 8
Output          : 0, 1, 1, 2, 3, 5, 8
*/

#include<stdio.h>
int main ()
{
int N;
int num1,num2,res;
    printf("Enter a number: ");
    scanf("%d",&N);
if ( N >= 0)
{
res=0;
num1=0;
num2=1;
while ( num1 <= N )
    {
    printf("%d, ",num1);
   
    res = num1 + num2;
    num1 = num2;
    num2 = res;
    }   
}
else
{
printf("Invalid input");
}
}
